<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <title>Order Confirmation - Awaiting Payment</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px
      auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .header { text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom:
      20px; } .header h1 { color: #333333; } .content { color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.6; } .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px; color: #999999; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <p>Dear Customer,</p>
        <p>Your order has been successfully confirmed, and we are currently
          awaiting payment to proceed further.</p>
        <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> {{orderId}}</p>
        <p>Once the payment is completed, we will process your order and notify
          you about the next steps.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing us!</p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>&copy; {{year}} Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>